With the tablet pre-installed with FM audio, you can also listen to the radio while navigating for your car. 【1920×1200 IPS Display+5MP+13MP Dual Cameras 】The tablet features a 10.1 inch G+G 10-point display with a high resolution of 1920 x 1200 IPS for a clearer viewing experience and faster touchscreen response. Equipped with a front camera (5 megapixels) and a rear camera (13 megapixels), you can easily enjoy shooting and video calls at any time. This Android tablet is the best gift for your kids and family for the New Year, Christmas, Thanksgiving, Mother's Day, Father's Day,etc.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fantastic tablet for a low price
reviews.reviewText: Looking for a tablet that looks and performs like the big brand tablets on the market? Look no further.I browsed Amazon and looked at more than a hundred different tablets. Most of the specs on them are horrible, however this tablet has excellent hardware and doesn't come preinstalled with a bunch of app bloat that you can't get rid of. It basically works right out of the box, comes with Android 12, and has a fast and sharp display. I bought two of these for my kids to play games and watch videos and this works great.The only negative for me was not having an option to buy a case specifically for this tablet. I had to go out and find a "generic 10" tablet" case which fits, but isn't perfect. Outside of that, I would highly recommend this to anyone else looking for a great tablet at a low price.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Exceeds My Expectations
reviews.reviewText: This "NO NAME" tablet really exceeded my expectations. My wife needed a simple tablet to access the internet and do minimal tasks on. This performs like the big brand names. Have always used Samsung products and this really surprised me. Didn't have a bunch of useless bloatware or extra apps on it. Set up was easy and has a great battery life. 64GB of storage which is actually more than my tablet has. Downfall is not having a specified case/screen protector for it.
